cdata.name: Solidified
cdata.desc:
Solidified is asmart contract security and development platform. Its main role is to act as adecentralized audit system and Bug Prediction Market. The platform intends to audit the users' smart contracts by following 4 main steps, multi-expert audit, fixes and verification, the bounty program andBug Prediction Market (on early 2019).

The Solid token is an Etherum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency developed by Solidified. The token can be used as a medium for purchase services within the platform.
